des:
Alexa and the Cherry products work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light. 

There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo. 

After connecting Alexa to your Cherry products in a few simple steps:

(1). Download our "Cherry IoT Solutions" app in android or IOS app market;
(2). Register one Cherry account in our "Cherry IoT Solutions" app;
(3). You need to have some Cherry devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our Cherry app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Cherry IoT Solutions" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, IOS or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Cherry IoT Solutions" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Cherry IoT Solutions", and you'll be navigated to Cherry login page;
(9). Input your Cherry account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
